articles.title: The Last Dinner Party crowned BBC Sound of 2024 winners - NME
articles.description: The Last Dinner Party have been named as the winners of BBC Radio 1’s Sound of 2024 poll of industry experts.
articles.content:
The Last Dinner Party have been named the winner of the BBCs Sound of 2024 poll.
